#

Pork Tenderloin Stir-Fry with Broccoli and Bell Peppers

30 min
$12.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

High-proteinNut-free

Cuisine:

Asian

Course:

Main

Tags:

Stir-fryQuick mealHealthy

Description

A quick and colorful stir-fry featuring tender pork, crunchy broccoli, and sweet bell peppers, packed with flavor!

Ingredients

  • pork tenderloin: 1 pound
  • broccoli florets: 2 cups
  • bell peppers (mixed colors): 2 cups
  • soy sauce: 1/4 cup
  • garlic (minced): 2 cloves
  • ginger (minced): 1 tablespoon
  • vegetable oil: 2 tablespoons
  • cornstarch: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • sesame oil: 1 teaspoon
